                    <p>A year after the World Cup, on August 8, 1987, Maradona participated in the match dedicated to the centenary of the English football League as part of the rest of the world team. For this match, Diego earned 100 thousand pounds. The game was played at Wembley, and when Maradona received the ball, there was a roar of dissatisfaction in the stands. After the game, Maradona said: "I don't blame the audience. What sometimes happened is the result of the unscrupulous work of a number of journalists...". 20 years later, Diego said, " The Hand of God never existed. God really helped us then, but I scored that ball with my hand." 22 years after the goal, Maradona apologized for his actions: "If I could go back in time and change history, I would do it. Right now, I can only apologize for what I did. What happened, happened, Argentina became the world champion, and I became the best football player on the planet."</p>
                    <p>&nbsp;</p>
                    <p><strong>Semi-final and final</strong></p>
                    <p>Before the semifinal matches, almost all the newspapers wrote that the winner could be one of two teams: either Argentina, led by Maradona, or France, the European champion, where Michel Platini shone. Before the semi-final game, Maradona said that he hoped that the Belgian defenders would not use illegal techniques against him. The game ended with a score of 2: 0, and Maradona, who became the best player of the meeting, scored both goals of his team, the second of which he scored after a pass, beating 4 players of the Belgian team. Immediately after the final whistle, Belgian goalkeeper Jean-Marie Pfaff quickly ran to the center of the field, where Maradona was, and exchanged shirts with him. Guy Thies, the head coach of the Belgian national team, said: "If Maradona played for our team — we would have reached the final. But you can only dream of such a thing."</p><div class="thumb tright" style="margin: 0.5em 0px 1.3em 1.4em; width: auto; background-color: #ffffff; clear: right; float: right; color: #222222; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;">
